			<p>
				Welcome to <span class="nm">gamelab</span>, a web application for online game theory experiments.
				<span class="nm">Gamelab</span> allows you to configure two-player normal-form games for play over the Internet.
				Participants accumulate tickets from their payoffs against the average play.
				At the end of the experiment, these tickets may be used in a lottery drawing to select winners.
			</p>
